[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    174[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mPer-cycle pseudonym discipline.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m "encoded_record_id: per-cycle pseudonym; not the source_record_id and not derived from the demographics" with the per-participant local mapping store retained at the participant only. This is the correct architectural primitive for preserving each participant's authority to resolve match results back to source records under its own access controls.[K
