[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    176[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe Why-This-Isn't-Production-Ready section names twelve gaps.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Trust-framework negotiation and contract drafting, salt-management ceremony and HSM custody, threshold calibration and approval governance, re-identification-risk review, three review queues with cohort-and-cycle-aware tooling, patient-consent capture and withdrawal pathways, information-blocking compliance posture, cross-organizational propagation policy, pilot evaluation infrastructure, idempotency and retry semantics, cohort-stratified accuracy monitoring discipline, compliance and operational ownership. The breadth is appropriate for a Complex-tier recipe.[K
