[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    342[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Variations / Active-learning-driven-configuration-tuning paragraph: "As the linkage-review queue resolves cases, the labels feed a periodic re-training of the matcher's thresholds and the per-feature weights. Active learning concentrates the review effort on the cases that most improve the downstream accuracy and the cohort fairness; over time, the review queue depth decreases as the matcher absorbs the labeled cases. The active-learning pattern is constrained by the encoded-data limitation (the labels are on the encoded records, not on the demographics; the calibration has to be careful not to leak demographic information through the labeling decisions)."[K
