[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    405[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mCC voice consistent throughout.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The opening research-conference vignette ("Two people are sitting at the same table at a research conference. One of them works for an academic medical center that runs a large diabetes outcomes study; the other works for a regional payer whose membership overlaps substantially with the academic medical center's patient panel. They have been talking for forty-five minutes about a research question they both want to answer") lands in the engineer-explaining-something-cool register exactly. The seven you-are-running-X scenarios that establish the operational landscape (multi-site clinical trial pharmacy-fill verification, state cancer registry social-determinant-and-mortality-detail enrichment, ACO out-of-network ED visit attribution, precision-oncology research consortium, post-state-law within-department public-health surveillance, TEFCA QHIN-of-QHINs Medicare-Medicaid national linkage, pharmaceutical-real-world-evidence with commercial tokenizer integration) are the recipe's strongest single passage of pacing on the cross-organizational landscape. Self-deprecating expertise lands well: "the cryptographic primitives are well-understood; the trust framework is the artifact that translates the primitives into an operational privacy guarantee, and the artifact has to be drafted by lawyers who understand both the cryptography and the institutional governance. Most institutions have no one on staff who fits both descriptions" is the recipe's strongest single observation about why PPRL succeeds or fails operationally. Parenthetical asides land well ("a refugee with a reconstructed identity" as the rare-DOB-instability case is the recipe's strongest single parenthetical aside; the eight-dimension enumeration's parentheticals on each dimension's operational content land at the right grain).[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    406[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mClinical and regulatory accuracy is strong.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The GLP-1 receptor agonist with MACE outcomes question is the correct active research question for the diabetes-outcomes-and-cardiac-events research community; type-2 diabetes baseline kidney function and weight as covariates is correct; the 24-month MACE measurement window is reasonable; the HIPAA Safe Harbor and Expert Determination de-identification standards are correctly framed as the regulatory framework PPRL operates within rather than as the framework PPRL replaces; 42 CFR Part 2 substance-use-treatment record applicability is correctly framed; post-Dobbs reproductive-health-care state-law overlays are correctly elevated; gender-affirming-care state-law overlay is correctly framed (recipe 5.7 upstream); the 21st Century Cures Act information-blocking interaction with PPRL-mediated research disclosures is correctly framed; the GDPR / PIPEDA / U.K. DPA cross-border applicability is correctly framed (and the inline TODO names the international-data-transfer landscape's evolution); the FDA Real-World Evidence Program reference is correctly granular; the CMS Patient Access API ecosystem framing is correctly future-looking.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    407[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mCryptographic accuracy is high.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The CLK construction is correctly attributed to the early-2010s record-linkage literature with refinements in [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140manonlink[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m; HMAC-SHA-256 with thirty parameterization keys derived from the salt is a correct construction for the per-Bloom-filter hashing; the Sørensen-Dice coefficient as the similarity measure is correctly framed as the workhorse for Bloom-filter comparison with Jaccard and Tversky as alternatives; the Vatsalan-Christen and Schnell-Borgs and Kuzu-et-al re-identification-attack literature is correctly cited; the random-hashing and balanced-encoding and hardening defensive measures are correctly framed; the homomorphic encryption family (Microsoft SEAL) and the SMPC protocol family (BGW, GMW, SPDZ) and the PSI primitive (OpenMined PSI) and the secret-sharing variants (Shamir, replicated, additive) are correctly framed as the third PPRL family with operational-feasibility caveats. The walk-through of the Bloom filter encoding (bigram tokenization, k cryptographic hash functions parameterized by the salt, bit positions in the array, Sørensen-Dice coefficient calculation with the ~0.94 / ~0.85 / ~0.18 calibration examples for "John Smith" vs "Jon Smith" / "Jane Smith" / "Maria Garcia") is the recipe's strongest single passage of cryptographic pedagogy.[K
