[49m[39m  414, 414[0m:[39m[49m **The booking is durable; the conversation is not.** Once the appointment is booked, the source of truth is the scheduling system. The conversation log is the audit trail of how the booking happened, but the appointment itself lives in the scheduling system. The bot's job after booking is to confirm successfully and make sure the patient understands what was booked; the bot is not the appointment's home.
